# Lyra Prompt Library

This folder contains modular prompt templates used by the Lyra agent to generate grant narratives, investor memos, ESG decks, and testimonial stories.

## Prompt Files

- `grant-starter.md` – Seed a basic grant narrative with emotional tone
- `investor-memo-draft.md` – Generate a first-pass investor summary
- `impact-testimonial.md` – Craft first-person community impact testimonials
- `esg-deck-narrative.md` – Build ESG-focused pitch narrative for slide decks
